OXG-Freebox-CodeBuilder-GPU-ACCELERATOR

This is an architecture for data-uptake which is captured/translated by a GPU and transferred to a GPU-ACCELERATOR combo-card system.
It uses a dedicated GPU and auxilliary ACCELERATOR card-setup which is interconnect.

The GPU-CARD involves a data-passthrough and is cycled to the GPU-chip.
The data is cycled in such a way that it is then recycled through modchips to the GPU over pllcx passthrough.
The data that is recycled is passthrough MODCHIP and GPU in alternation, or from MODCHIP to MODCHIP before being recycled to yet another GPU alternation. For which it is phased in such a way as described:
Main Pass to Gpu Phase
PowerPhase pass to Gpu
Encode Pass to Gpu
Priority/Organize/Storage/Queue Pass to Gpu
Permute-Mod Pass to Gpu
Logic-Mod Pass to Gpu
Re-Logic-Mod Pass to Gpu

Then is template/prepsheet for the pass to accelerator
The accelerator then decodes the template/prepsheet as it is fed from the gpu-card or its link-out/cross-link
This connection allows the accelerator to recalculate the gpu-data as to matchbase its virtualzied codestate (otherwise it works as well as a default sub-processor/sub-gpu non-dedicated/support-only : also not recommended due to potential conflict/issue with actual quantum data as intended/against the manufacture/purpose of the accelerator itself---which is to simply decode pipeline/acceleration fed by a template/prepsheet)
The accelerator then integrates the data into the codestate and shells it to the cpu which shells it to the ram/driver for call.
as stated, the cpu then allocates the codestate as needed for the onboard-driver for which interfaces with the cpu, it sources/origins the driver-data for the meta-engine/meta-image in host/support if in pipeline/acceleration of that feedback/loophole i.e. the game-space.

The driver is tailored for the setup of a Gpu/Acceleration combined virtual codestate in which the cpu interfaces. And the driver can incorporate cpu-integration through which further data is pipelined into feed/loop of the intended chains/scripts for which are programmed by the corresponding meta-image. 
This renders a desired platform/flagship to the source/origin of the data given, whether meta/generated or otherwise. (as is considered re-coded)

--The crosslink/link-out is generally the process/service chain which is the connection achieved (important with meta-iamges to be compatible or expected/evaluated)
This will cloudworks/drone-society/zen-mode/dumb-mode as necessary.
